" Pull My Heart Away " by Jack Pe√±ate RECEPTION Section::::Reception .
Charlie St. Cloud received generally negative reviews from critics .
On Rotten Tomatoes the film has an approval rating of 27 % based on 124 reviews with an average rating of 4.6/10 .
The site 's critical consensus reads , " Zac Efron gives it his all , but Charlie St. Cloud is too shallow and cloying to offer much more than eye candy for his fans . "
On Metacritic , the film has a score of 37 out of 100 based on 30 critics , indicating " generally unfavorable reviews " .
Audiences polled by CinemaScore gave the film an average grade of " B+ " on an A+ to F scale .
